  "title": "Carpenter / Installer (Building Finishing) #81691",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Building Completion and Finishing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Carpenter / Installer (Building Finishing)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Woodlands</li><li>Working Hours: 6 days (Monday – Saturday, 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + AWS + Bonus + OT Pay</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Read drawings or work instructions and confirm measurements before starting work.</li><li>Carry out carpentry works such as fabrication, assembly, and installation (e.g., cabinets, doors, frames, panels, and fittings).</li><li>Use hand tools and power tools safely for cutting, drilling, sanding, and finishing.</li><li>Install and align items properly to meet quality standards and site requirements.</li><li>Repair or adjust carpentry items when needed.</li><li>Coordinate with supervisors and site teams to complete tasks on schedule.</li><li>Keep the work area clean and follow workplace safety procedures.</li><li>Support other site tasks assigned by the supervisor.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the department head</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Relevant carpentry experience in renovation, interior, or building finishing works.</li><li>Able to read basic drawings and take accurate measurements.</li><li>Comfortable with hands-on work, including lifting and moving materials safely.</li><li>Familiar with common carpentry tools and safe work practices.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81691 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
